.vscode/**
src/**
scripts/**
node_modules/**
# Ship only the SDK's JS (sdk.mjs, ~4.5MB). Its per-platform native binaries
# (@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk-*, 200MB+) are intentionally excluded — the
# extension spawns the user's own installed `claude` instead.
!node_modules/@anthropic-ai/claude-agent-sdk/**
**/tsconfig.json
**/esbuild.js
**/*.map
**/*.ts
.gitignore
